  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> You used Shield Block to prevent damage from an adjacent creature's attack.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>As you absorb a blow from an enemy, you can use their attack's momentum against them. Attempt to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.lOE4yjUnETTdaf2T]{Reposition} the creature whose attack you used Shield Block against. You don't need to have a hand free to do so. You gain a +1 item bonus to the Athletics check if your shield is at least 4th level, a +2 item bonus if your shield is at least 10th level, and a +3 item bonus if your shield is at least 16th level.</p>"
